{
  "_comment": "sovereign-os selfdef disk-usage dashboard. Visualizes selfdef_disk_usage_* gauges (selfdef commit 694b611). Pairs with 5 alerts. Disk-fill detection — IPS-spine integrity hazard surveillance.",
  "annotations": {"list": []},
  "editable": true,
